Maximum Length of a Data Extension Field Has Changed
Engagement Data Retention and Access Policy Is Changing

Data extension field limits in Contact Builder are now 255 characters. Send and engagement data is now retained for 180 days.

Maximum Length of a Data Extension Field Has Changed
To improve performance, the length of the field chosen in send relationships is now limited to 255 characters in Contact Builder.
Engagement Data Retention and Access Policy Is Changing
Beginning January 15, 2025, the retention period for send and engagement data is limited to 180 days. Data exceeding this period is deleted.
